57 Section 4. It is not the intent of this act to make
58 appropriations, but the appropriations required by this act
59 shall be made in the annual budget act for the affected
60 entities.
61 Section 5. This act shall become effective immediately
62 upon its passage and approval by the Governor, or upon its
63 otherwise becoming a law.
